<subSubSection id="9AC9AB4F6130B4BEE2B1EABDFC0FBB5E" pageId="null" pageNumber="594" type="description">
<paragraph id="794CE1E87B173877532EEF52FEB661AD" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">
Unterscheidet sich von der nahe verwandten 
<taxonomicName id="B5621756B4A56F0B49364132FB46335A" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Vicia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="594" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="narbonensis">
<emphasis id="459D42B22F5787B3D1D3BEBEA38F3CDF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">V. narbonensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 16) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="B05AA588B442BE82CE0CE61F1BD00430" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">
<normalizedToken id="A2871AA895B6BFF57C8310FE85B4610D" originalValue="Teilblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">Teilblaetter</normalizedToken>
der obern 
<normalizedToken id="295C93171CD1B007A21EAB8847AEB89E" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="FD0E6514563DE06C388D26DA9D927134" originalValue="Nebenblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">Nebenblaetter</normalizedToken>
scharf 
<normalizedToken id="25FBEB477E8745F9D8A7A4F8007C7B36" originalValue="gezähnt" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">gezaehnt</normalizedToken>
</emphasis>
(bei allen andern Arten des Gebiets 
<normalizedToken id="48F9D48C23D509580DF922DFDD709C9F" originalValue="Teilblätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">Teilblaetter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="12A26EE44FF023826008337FE340C486" originalValue="±" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">+/-</normalizedToken>
ganzrandig). - 
<normalizedToken id="8CDC2A84B2DAD2B825113486E9910C9A" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="A4FB8C1ED36FD8DD2153445214223691" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="CC1EC7B8C0C7E0738D2C26875EAA63EA" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="66CE47CC9C5219A45B90B3072EE47E87" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">
<emphasis id="B3E8767E99F31D0B81AA614EE3AB4903" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="EE503913C07C662C8FAD007F993955BF" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">14:</emphasis>
Material unbekannter Herkunft (Sveshnikova 1927).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="B013B005CA6443D5221EB29283E3340C" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">
<emphasis id="08E1F869039AF0D29227CF7253F1FAFB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">Standort.</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="4D05DD66E6B4A3ADD2B36B100E6CF9A0" originalValue="Ähnlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">Aehnlich</normalizedToken>
wie 
<taxonomicName id="5D4BA30788FCC85F9768D799A7F2BCEB" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Vicia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="594" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="narbonensis">
<emphasis id="0B7F55AA9A0B4339B9C1A36D77F8CB53" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">V. narbonensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 16).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4A6653BCD8F190614FD640804C0A6EF6" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">
<emphasis id="0B6619A9662ACFA80F9AB9397BE7A6FC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">Verbreitung. Mediterrane Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="073EB21946C5509668999501E095E146" originalValue="Ähnlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">Aehnlich</normalizedToken>
wie 
<taxonomicName id="327B8ED6C293FEF835845517F9BC6DC8" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Vicia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="594" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="narbonensis">
<emphasis id="499FF9140446244A060FC057DDF5B519" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">V. narbonensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 16). - Im Gebiet selten eingeschleppt, z.B. Wintzenheim im 
<normalizedToken id="B408B9E387BA4EBFC8EE8B09CBD71C08" originalValue="Elsaß" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">Elsass</normalizedToken>
, sonst selten angebaut.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F82415FF6FEBD2CD0CFDC5E552DF2654" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">
<emphasis id="1E80BA57D34E487B27D8E5E21494DAC9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Der systematische Wert der 
<taxonomicName id="ACADC0EE6A8399DB4F6F248D0F79A35F" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Vicia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="594" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="serratifolia">
<emphasis id="541887FDD29DB4601B696ED73EB0E42E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">V. serratifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="0C50AF74C17FB311F24916C01A554C3D" originalValue="muß" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">muss</normalizedToken>
noch 
<normalizedToken id="134D333B1FFD63B09DC002392E0C7391" originalValue="überprüft" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">ueberprueft</normalizedToken>
werden. Nach Sveshnikova (1927) soll die Chromosomenmorphologie sich stark von jener von 
<taxonomicName id="39BC42D6FACB5D67A09220228C34B1F3" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Vicia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="594" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="narbonensis">
<emphasis id="F4632951A05B7B92EFF7824F5DBE3A63" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="594">V. narbonensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 16) unterscheiden und eine Bastardierung zwischen beiden Sippen nicht gelungen sein.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
